OL,6,FA new ITV drama will lay bare the
OL,7,Fsacrifices doctors made during the
OL,8,Fpandemic - its writer Dr Rachel Clarke
OL,9,Fand star Joanne Froggatt talk to ITV
OL,10,FNews' Entertainment Editor Nina Nannar
OL,12,FDr Rachel Clarke is determined not to
OL,13,Fget emotional when we chat about the
OL,14,Fnew ITV drama Breathtaking, which is
OL,15,Fbased on her book of the same name.
