OL,3,CITV's Breathtaking is a chilling view
OL,4,Cof Covid wards by a doctor who lived it
OL,6,FIt led her to retell her experiences
OL,7,Fin a book, which she has adapted,
OL,8,Falongside Line Of Duty creator Jed
OL,9,FMercurio and The Crown actor Prasanna
OL,10,FPuwanarajah who were both junior
OL,11,Fdoctors before moving into TV.
OL,13,FThe hard-hitting drama will be shown
OL,14,Fon three consecutive nights next week,
OL,15,Fwith Joanne Froggatt playing Rachel
OL,16,FClarke as she frantically tried to
OL,17,Fcope with what was coming.
