OL,3,CITV's Breathtaking is a chilling view
OL,4,Cof Covid wards by a doctor who lived it
OL,6,FTo play the role the former Downton
OL,7,FAbbey actress underwent a form of
OL,8,Fmedical bootcamp, Froggatt says, to
OL,9,Fget the language and the terminology
OL,10,Fcorrect.
OL,12,FMuch of the series is filmed in long
OL,13,Fcontinuous shots, with Froggatt racing
OL,14,Fdown corridors, from one medical
OL,15,Femergency to another and the end
OL,16,Fresult is chillingly realistic.
OL,18,FI asked her what she learned from
OL,19,Fplaying a Covid doctor in Rachel's
OL,20,Fdrama, and what she found particularly
OL,21,Fshocking.
